parameters:
\c[10]Demon God Devill\c[0], you've come this
far... I am Devill indeed, you could even say you
are... a living replica of that magical girl...

\c[10]After the creation of the heavens and the
earth, the demon god Devill, imprisoned in the
depths of hell, gave birth to demons and brought
chaos into the world, driven solely by its deep-
seated resentment.\c[0]

\c[10]The demon god Devill\c[0] pushed the war god
Digret to the brink, and just when it seemed like
the end was near, a magical girl appeared... I
believe her name was Kurashimamiri...

\c[10]The power of the demon god Devill\c[0] was
overwhelming... It repelled our army and
completely separated this region, which is the
entrance to hell and the location of the Astalot
Labyrinth, from the rest of the continent.

\c[10]The demon god Devill\c[0] And thus, Grimoire
Land was created... You are, without a doubt, the
very embodiment of that magical girl, aren't
you...?

What are you talking about? I have a proper name,
you know. My name is Konoha.

Besides, my memories have come back quite a bit...
This place, it's not the world I belong to, that's
what it means.

In this world, some of the residents are women who
have been reincarnated from another world and
become magical girls, while men become demons...

I came to this world to find a man who got lost
from the original world. That man is Leonid, the
king of my homeland, also known as Gardis Leon...

Devill, you're talking about Leon, I remember that
voice...

\c[10]Demon God Devill\c[0]... Kuhahaha... Have
you come to tell me that you have been
reincarnated? I have wandered beneath here for
thousands of years...

\c[10]Demon God Devill\c[0], you are a marvel to
me... To think that even after your resurrection,
you would be confronted by that magical girl from
back then.

\c[10]Demon God Devill\c[0]: I won't allow anyone
to interfere anymore. In this world where there is
no detestable Bureianodo, I shall reign supreme.

I won't let that happen. Leon, please... Wake
up... You're not someone like Devill.

\c[10]Demon Lord Devill\c[0], it seems further
conversation is futile... Show me the true power
of a demon.

There's no choice but to do it. With this sword...
I'm sure I can defeat Devill... and save Leon...!

\c[10]Devill the Demon Lord\c[0], come forth!
Magical girl Kurashimamiri... With centuries of
grudges, I will eradicate you!
Leon! It really is Leon after all!
Thank goodness...! I finally found you...

Why have you become a child?! Then, aren't you
just like me?
Leon, it's obviously your fault, isn't it?
I see... So I have returned to this world again.

That's right. In order to bring you back, I have
to return from this world of books that I came all
the way to.

I have to return from here... I'm certain, I have
to... conclude the ending of the book... but...
ugh...

I see, Konoha went this far for my sake... I'm
happy, but... it seems it can't be that simple.

No... It's because of my reincarnation that the
existence known as the Devil... in other words, I
am also that Devil... There is no change in the
fact that we are one and the same.

Looking at the entrance of that abyss... The Devil
doesn't seem to fall from there, it's waiting for
me.

Yeah. I'm not Leon anymore. I have to fall into
the abyss. Otherwise... this book will never reach
its conclusion.

If that happens, you won't be able to go back.
Don't make such a sad face, Konoha.

It's my responsibility for getting myself trapped
in this world of the grimoire. I have to take
responsibility for it properly.
Why... did it have to turn out like this...

Thank you, Konoha. I'm really happy to be able to
reunite like this. Please say hello to everyone in
the country for me...
過去の記憶（テキストのみ）

Ugh...! This voice... it's someone's... memory...
why now...?

\c[10]Demon Lord Devil\c[0] Fuhahahaha...!
Finally... the day has come to defeat... Classima
Mili...

\c[10]Konoha, who has become the vessel for the
Demon Lord Devil... hehe... very well, as a
special treat, I shall personally impregnate you
with my seed.

\c[10]Demon Lord Devil\c[0] And give birth to the
most wicked and evil demon...!

particle clear sinen-EID this sinen below

No... I can't let them die anymore, I have to
help...

Wildcat, I'm counting on your strength. I believe
in you, so we can do this, right?

I'm glad... I was saved... I was about to give up
again...

Konoha, you're quite forceful... Well, that's one
of your good points though...

Leon, you should rest here for now. I still have
things that I need to take care of.

Are you planning to find other endings, by any
chance?
Yes, I see. I need to find a way...
Ah... this voice... is it from that time?!
You've done well to make it this far... However...

By rescuing Leon, the story has not yet reached
its conclusion... The wonders of the end still
remain...

I wonder if it's about time you tell me who you
really are.

I am Kurashima Mili. I am the first magical girl
in this world.

So, you're... the magical girl that Devil was
talking about... You've been inside this sword all
along?!
Yes, I have been supporting you for this day.

I am extremely grateful to you for putting in so
much effort to save me from the crisis of the end.

However... that end is approaching... right before
our eyes.

What do you mean...? Earlier, you said that
rescuing Leon wouldn't bring about the
conclusion...

If I rescue Leon, does that mean the end you
mentioned will come?

Yes, that's right. It's just one possible outcome,
but you denied it.

We must prepare for a different outcome... It's
not ideal, but by manifesting here now, problems
have arisen.
Ahh... I-I've been caught, haven't I...

Wait, why is Gilcho here!? There's no way they
could come to a place like this...

Konoha, this person is calling themselves Gilcho,
but in reality, they are someone else.

This person is none other than Maleus, the one who
will bring about the end of this world.

Hehehe, strictly speaking, I'm a little different
from the real Maleus. I'm more like a spiritual
entity.
Maleus, the court mage of Gardis?!

This person has been waiting for me to manifest,
and it seems their purpose is to bring about my
ultimate demise, right? Maleus.

In general, that's how it is. This Grimoire Land
has become too bloated.

Who would have thought that a mere story of a
grimoire would become such a vast world.

The illegal element that infiltrated this world,
that would be the existence known as magical
girls. Thanks to them, even I myself have found it
difficult to bring this story to an end.

It would be problematic for me, the actual entity,
to enter the Grimoire, so I have entered this
world as a spiritual entity.
Why do we have to bring an end to this world?

What's the point of an endless story? No one can
bring this story to an end. In that case, as the
author myself, I have no choice but to do it.

So, Maleus, you're the one who created this
grimoire called Grimoire Land, right...

Well, it's about time, Kurashima Mili. Konoha,
let's bring this world to an end and you will
return to your original world.

However, if you defeat me and choose to leave this
world behind, you will never be able to return to
your original world.

Konoha, it's up to you... the fate of this
world... I entrust it to you...

(If we choose the end of this world, \C[6] we can
return to the original world... \C[0] If we choose
to leave this world, \C[10] we cannot go
back\C[0])
Choose the end of the world

I choose the end. My true purpose is to take Leon
back with me.

Ah... I see... That's how it will be... It's very
disappointing...

I'm glad you accepted my words, Konoha. But
Kurashima Mili won't forgive you.

It can't be helped... I came here to bring Leon
back to the original world, after all!

I will leave the world. Even if I can't return to
the original world, I can't bring myself to erase
this Grimoire Land.

What!? What did you say? Are you serious? You
won't be able to go back?

I see. But it doesn't mean I'll die. I was able to
rescue Leon. That alone is enough.

Besides, even though it was a short time, I can't
bring myself to erase this Grimoire Land.

Ah... Konoha... I believed that you would surely
say that...

*sigh*... Konoha, you are so foolish... Choosing
to preserve this world... it means that sacrifices
will continue to increase...

You should have seen the tragedies of magical
girls, too... Are you saying it's okay for them to
increase even more...?

I will definitely put an end to that. I will
change the world so that magical girls can be
happy.

It won't change! It has continued for thousands of
years... If we don't meet our end here, the
tragedies will continue...!

It seems... we won't be able to understand each
other... I'm disappointed, to think you would make
such a choice...

Very well, I will show you the power of the
creator of this world. I will make both Konoha and
Kurashima Mili disappear here.

particle set nest-EID this nest below

Konoha...! Be careful... The opponent possesses
tremendous power.
◆◆◆◆◆◆「かかってきなさい」「軽くひねってあげるわ」◆◆◆◆◆◆

After coming this far, I won't lose, Maleus! Let's
settle this!
particle clear nest-EID this nest below

......Ugh...... It seems that it's not like
before......
I hope you don't regret it... Konoha...
深淵へ落ちていくマレウス

Ah... Finally... The awe of the end has
vanished...

Kurashima Mili, what will you do? You won't be
able to reside in this sword anymore, right?

Yes, that's right. Originally, I no longer exist
as a physical being. I am just lingering as a
similar thought form to Maleus...

It's an incredible amount of energy...! What is
this...! That is...
(This is definitely... from a man named Donoan...)

It's the treasure of resurrection... That gem...
It possesses an extraordinary power... Yes, it is
the very power of Bureianodo.

No way, that man named Donoan...! Are you saying
he was the Bureianodo itself...?!

If I remember correctly, Bureianodo is the god of
creation in this world? Ah! The gem is moving on
its own!
particle set devil this devil below

Wahahahaha! This...! This is delightful! The
sinking me and Devil... have fused together!!!

Why is Bureianodo...! It's supposed to be the
enemy of Devil...

It seems luck was on my side... Witness the
overflowing power of this magic!
This is on a whole different level...

I see, with the power of Devil... there is nothing
to fear... right?!
Konoha! Don't let go of your sword!

You let your guard down, huh? Both Konoha and
Kurashima Mili are finished.

Oh... so this is the wretched sword known as
Wildcat... How pathetic... This is what they call
a reversal of fortune...
Ugh... My body... But... I can still move...
There's no way I'll let you escape! Ahahahaha!!!

With this sword that has helped you until now,
Konoha, I shall let you meet your end.
All hope is lost... I guess...

Fuhahahaha! It's over!! Next is Kurashima Mili,
you...

Huh... What is this...?! The outfit is
different...

I'm sorry for staying silent until now, this is my
true form...

What the hell happened...?! I should have
definitely finished them off...!

Magical girls \C[22]transform\C[0] for moments
like this. That's why all magical girls have
sealed this ability.

The demons led by Devil always come into existence
with greater power after assessing the power of
magical girls.

Until this moment arrived, it was necessary to
hide this transformation.

Everything is to completely destroy you, Devil,
without sending you to the abyss.

Wha... To... annihilate me... You've been waiting
for thousands of years for this...?

Even if you are defeated normally, demons will
only return to the abyss. But if we can destroy
Devil itself, demons will not be born.

Konoha, please. With your current abilities, you
can destroy Devil...!

Is this... the true form of a magical girl? It's
unbelievable how much power is welling up.

I won't forgive you...! Bureianōdo... once again,
you have... trapped me...

So, the intention was to deliberately bring me
back from the abyss in order to destroy me... Very
well, if that's the case, let's bet our existence,
me and the magical girls, and fight.

......Ugh...... It seems like it's the same as
before......
I hope you don't regret it... Konoha...
深淵へ落ちていくマレウス

Ah... Finally... The awe of the end has
disappeared...

Kurashima Mili, what will you do? You won't be
able to reside in this sword anymore, right?

Yes, that's right. I no longer exist physically, I
am just a lingering consciousness, similar to
Maleus.

My role is to continue watching over the
reincarnators from now on.

That's how it is. Well then... I guess I have no
choice but to return to Grimoire Land with Leon.

Leon, it's over. I want to say let's go home,
but...

To put it bluntly, we can't go back anymore,
neither me nor Leon.

But, this world isn't so bad either. Without a
ruler, Reingarnet will become difficult.

I wonder what will happen to the demons. It'll be
easier without them, won't it?

Well... I guess it doesn't matter where we go, as
long as I have Konoha's small breasts.

Who has small breasts!!! They're definitely
there!!!

Geez, enough already! Since I won't be a queen or
anything anymore, I'll work properly!

Ah... to think that my magical girl... would end
up losing...
particle set cat-EID this cat below

I can't just let myself be done like this...!
Kurasu Mami... it's time to settle this.

It's a sad thing, but I won't let this world be
erased... there's no other choice.
particle clear cat-EID this cat below

Ah... Ahh... To be destroyed... by Konoha's
hands...
Well... that might actually be a good thing...

With this, it's finally over. The end will begin
shortly.

Konoha, and Leon too, should be able to return to
their original world. A dimensional portal should
appear.

Yes, it's time to say goodbye to this Grimoire
Land.

The sacrifices caused by this Grimoire were too
many. Finally, we can put an end to it...

Please make sure to tell my original world self to
never create a world like this again,
unnecessarily.
Yes, I will definitely make sure to tell them.
Leon, it's over. Let's go home.

Konoha, it's amazing how you came all the way here
to help.

Oh, what are you saying? Leon came to help me too,
so I pushed myself.
Ahaha, there were also... things like that.

I see... I also want to return to my original
body...
particle set devil this devil below

Kurashima Mili, leave the rest to me. I'll unleash
all of my power on that person.

Come! Magical Girl Konoha! I'll kill you and end
this!

This is the real deal, let's go for the final
battle!
particle clear devil this devil below

It's over... I can't sense the presence of the
Devil anymore...

I... really thought it was over... Was being
stabbed with a sword the trigger for this
transformation?

That's how it turned out. I did give a brief
explanation at the very beginning, but I couldn't
let you use this transformation...

Saving the trump card until the very end, huh? By
the way, Baretta, about that...

Bureianōdo is the creator god of this world, but
originally, they were fighting against that Devil
at the bottom of this abyss.

The surviving Bureianōdo was able to emerge from
this abyss and breathe life into this world,
creating a replica of the world.

No one knew what happened to him over the long
years, but to think that he was living as a
resident of this world...

It turned out to be a good thing that I helped
Donoan. Well then, from now on, I will...

Since we can't go back anymore, we have no choice
but to stay in this world. It's a relief that Leon
is safe though...

No, there should be a way. Even if Maleus isn't
here, it shouldn't matter.

Do you remember the wording of the method to
return to the world originally?

If I remember correctly... weaving the conclusion
of the story... is the condition?

That's right. The conclusion refers to a world
without worries for Maleus. If it's that kind of
ending, even without an end, we should be able to
bring the story to a close...
But I defeated the Devil. Is that not enough?

That's right. The abyss leading to hell is still
there. Even though there is nothing now, we don't
know what will cause a disaster to arise.
We need to completely close the abyss hole.
C-Closing something like this... but how?!

There is no other way but for someone to enter and
close it from the inside.

In the end, someone has to become a sacrifice,
huh...

If we close this, peace will come to this world
and the story will end. However, it is not the
end, so the world will not come to an end.

And those who have come to this world, the so-
called magical girls who have been reincarnated as
demons, will all be able to return to their
original world.

I will close it. As long as Leon can return to the
original world, I don't mind.

It's not like I have a strong attachment to the
original world, and I've had quite a bit of fun
here.

Is it okay? If we close the abyss, it will never
open again, and we will live eternally at the
bottom of hell.

It's okay, I'm kinda used to that stuff, so I'll
manage somehow.

I understand. I respect Konoha's feelings, but
there is also the option of staying in this world.
No, it's okay. Please teach me how to do it.

Well then, it's like floating there... After that,
it's like pulling the door in with magic power.
I see. Alright then, please take care of Leon.
Konoha-san, you forgot something. Hand it over.

You're really kind, aren't you? It's obvious that
this is my role.
What stupid thing are you saying! No way!

(I'm glad I could meet you... You are the true
magical girl that I admired... Thank you,
Konoha...)

Kukuku... The devil inside me is saying... I will
make you a breeding ground and continue to give
birth to the strongest demons...
